        ( ( A ^ 2 ) + ( B ^ 2 ) ) = ( C ^ 2 ) ) ) $=
      ( cn wcel wa cv c2 cexp co cmul wceq caddc wrex wo cvv cc cpr cmin w3a wb
      oprex preq12bg mpanr12 anbi1d andir df-3an orbi12i bitr4i syl6bb 2rexbidv
      rexbidv r19.43 2rexbii rexbii 3bitri wi pythagtriplem1 3ancoma sylbi nncn
