  ${
    pythagtriplem11.1 $e |- M = ( ( ( sqr ` ( C + B ) ) + ( sqr ` ( C - B ) ) )
        / 2 ) $.
    $( Lemma for ~ pythagtrip .  Show that ` M ` (which will eventually be
       closely related to the ` m ` in the final statement) is a natural.
       (Contributed by Scott Fenton, 17-Apr-2014.) $)
    pythagtriplem11 $p |- ( ( ( A e. NN /\ B e. NN /\ C e. NN ) /\
